languages.text: "Слышали, ребятки, сам{mf||а} Лорд-капитан от нас дел ждет. А {mf|его|ее} подвести никак нельзя". {n}Подельники одобрительно гудят.{/n} "Мы ваш наказ исполним в точности".

traits.locale_text: "Слышали, ребятки, сам{mf||а} Лорд-капитан от нас дел ждет. А {mf|его|ее} подвести никак нельзя". {n}Подельники одобрительно гудят.{/n} "Мы ваш наказ исполним в точности".

languages.text: "Hear that, boys? The Lord Captain {mf|himself|herself} is expecting good things from us. We can't let {mf|him|her} down." {n}His cronies make sounds of approval.{/n} "We will fulfil your command to the letter."

languages.text: 「聞いたか、お前たち？ロード・キャプテンは我々に良いことを期待している。陛下を失望させるわけにはいかない」{n}彼の取り巻きが賛同の声を上げる。{/n}「我々はあなたの命令を忠実に実行します」
languages.original_text: "Hear that, boys? The Lord Captain {mf|himself|herself} is expecting good things from us. We can't let {mf|him|her} down." {n}His cronies make sounds of approval.{/n} "We will fulfil your command to the letter."

languages.text: “听到了吗，小伙子们？舰长大人本人可在看着咱们呢，咱们可不能让{mf|他|她}失望。”{n}他的手下发出了欢呼声。{/n}“我们会忠实地执行您的命令。”
languages.original_text: "Hear that, boys? The Lord Captain {mf|himself|herself} is expecting good things from us. We can't let {mf|him|her} down." {n}His cronies make sounds of approval.{/n} "We will fulfil your command to the letter."

languages.text: "Habt ihr gehört, Jungs? Der Lord Captain höchstselbst erwartet gute Dinge von uns. Wir dürfen {mf|ihn|sie} nicht enttäuschen." {n}Seine Handlanger murmeln zustimmend.{/n} "Wir werden Euren Befehl exakt ausführen."

languages.text: « Vous entendez ça, les gars ? {mf|Le seigneur-capitaine lui-même|La seigneure-capitaine elle-même} compte sur nous. On peut pas {mf|le|la} laisser tomber. » {n}Ses comparses approuvent bruyamment.{/n} « On suivra vos ordres à la lettre. »

languages.text: "Duydunuz mu beyler? Lord Kaptan, bizden iyi şeyler yapmamızı bekliyor. Onu hayal kırıklığına uğratamayız." {n}Ahbapları arasından onaylayan sesler yükseliyor.{/n} "Emrinizi harfiyen yerine getireceğiz."
